<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .email-header h1 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .email-body p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #007BFF;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Support Request Received</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hi <span class="highlight"><%= enquiry.name %></span>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for reaching out to us. This is to confirm that we have received your support request.</p>
        <p>Your request has been logged with the reference ID <span class="highlight"><%= enquiry.formatted_id %></span>. Please include this reference in any future communication.</p>
        <p>Our team is currently reviewing your request and will update you as soon as possible</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing <span class="highlight">NikoNiko</span>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; NikoNiko. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>